data.title: Shahid Kapoor shares first look from 'Deva', film to release on Dussehra 2024
meta_keywords: r rajkumar full movie hindi shahid kapoor 2013
data.meta_description: On Dussehra, Shahid Kapoor surprised his audience by revealing the first look from his upcoming movie, Deva. He added that the movie's release would be on Dussehra the following year. The movie will release worldwide in theatres on October 11, 2024. The actor sports a more muscular appearance and looks dapper in a white shirt and beige trousers, along with shorter hair and beard.  Shahid's outfit hints that the actor is playing a cop in Deva. He is also seen wearing a pendant which looks like a ring. Sharing the picture on Instagram, Shahid made the announcement as he wrote, DEVA in theatres on Dussehra 11th October 2024. Watch the  video....
